title: LAZY MAN'S BREAD
description:
Jack Scalfani shows you how to make bread in 60 seconds. Be sure to subscribe to his show and his new channel "Jack on the Go" http://youtube.com/jackonthego
Here's the recipe:
4 cups all purpose flour
1/4 teaspoon dry yeast
1 tablespoon salt
2 cups warm water
